        },
        "progressBar": true
    },
    "slides": [
        {
            "type": "main",
            "id": "Cover",
            "title": "Shower Presentation Engine",
            "background": "pictures/cover.jpg"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "title": "Idea",
            "content": [
                "Cleaver but better"
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "title": "Cleaver",
            "content": [
                "Open source from Jordan Scales",
                "Node.js server with local JSON file",
                "[github.com/prezjordan/cleaver](http://github.com/prezjordan/cleaver)",
                "Example: [http://prezjordan.github.io/cleaver](http://prezjordan.github.io/cleaver/)"
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "title": "Whats Wrong?",
            "content": [
                "Too specific for \"normal people\""
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "title",
            "title": "Shower was found"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "title": "Whats Wrong with Shower?",
            "content": [
                "Still too specific for \"normal people\"",
                "Have to know how to edit HTML to make a presentation"
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "title": "What we ~<del~>wanted to do~</del~> did",
            "content": [
                {
                    "bullets": [
                        "JSON support",
                        "Bug fixes",
                        "Ability to switch themes",
                        "Mobile*"
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "footnote": "* Mobile is iffy on some browsers."
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "title": "Shower is pretty well featured...",
            "content": [
                "Text",
                {
                    "bullets": [
                        "Lists",
                        "Lists of stuff",
                        {
                            "numlist": [
                                "Such as lists of lists",
                                "[Links](http://google.com) _and_ **formatters**"
                            ]
                        },
                        "And HTML formatting support..."
                    ]
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "title": "Embed HTML",
            "content": [
                "~<iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/6A5EpqqDOdk\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen~>~</iframe~>"
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "timer": 5,
            "title": "Then, Timers!",
            "content": [
                "Count to 5"
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "title",
            "title": "And images!",
            "background": "pictures/picture.jpg"
        },
        {
            "type": "title",
            "title": "JSON>>Support"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "title": "How to use JSON with Shower",
            "content": [
                "Add this line:",
                {
                    "code": [
                        {
                            "codeline": [
                                "<",
                                {
                                    "marked": "meta"
                                },
                                " name=\"showerJsonSource\""
                            ]
                        },
                        "      content=\"../json/Presentation.json\">"
                    ]
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "title",
            "title": "And you're done (with JSON)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "title": "Bug fixes",
            "content": [
                {
                    "bullets": [
                        "General functionality",
                        "Backspace support",
                        "Clicking timed slide didn't work"
                    ]
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "title": "Theme switching",
            "content": [
                "Swap between themes",
                {
                    "footnote": "We only have 2 themes, both of which come with Shower."
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "title": "Mobile phones",
            "content": [
